- Soga-san.
- Ah, hello.

129
00:06:47,590 --> 00:06:48,400
Haa...

130
00:06:56,840 --> 00:06:58,520
- I feel refreshed.
- No, that was too early!

131
00:06:58,770 --> 00:06:59,863
You must go back and forth

132
