143
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:26,130
At the very least,

144
00:07:26,290 --> 00:07:28,211
I can guarantee that

145
00:07:28,236 --> 00:07:29,916
Sakae really likes you.

146
00:07:32,350 --> 00:07:35,420
