That's it, Soga-san!

212
00:10:21,140 --> 00:10:22,304
Alright, let's establish

213
00:10:22,328 --> 00:10:23,446
the rules in detail.

214
00:10:23,585 --> 00:10:24,155
Sure.

215
00:10:24,180 --> 00:10:25,160
Yeah.

216
